# Entra ID (Azure AD) single sign-on for the frontend.
# Leave blank to run in local demo sign-in mode.
# To enable real Microsoft SSO:
#   1. Register a Single-Page Application in Entra ID.
#   2. Add a redirect URI equal to this app's origin (e.g. http://localhost:5173).
#   3. Set the values below and restart `npm run dev`.
VITE_AAD_CLIENT_ID=
# Tenant: "organizations" (any work/school account), "common", or a specific tenant GUID/domain.
VITE_AAD_TENANT=organizations
